var tipuesearch = {"pages":[{"url":"./pages/about/","text":"2016Fall 修課成員網誌","title":"About","tags":"misc"},{"url":"./2017-04-21shang-ke-nei-rong-lian-xi.html","text":"在Virtualbox中,以橋接網路卡設定,建立一台 Ubuntu伺服主機 sudo apt update幫我們把下載的網站資料update到最新,如果不行就用 sudo rm /var/lib/dpkg/lock 把lock刪除掉 , sudo apt install nginx 安裝nginx ,用ifconfig再到外部的瀏覽器打上IP:80就可以看到,如果像要知道檔案在哪裡就 cd /var/www/html , ls -l ,sudo vi index.nginx-debian.html 就可更改 上課內容練習 from 陳士正 on Vimeo .","title":"2017-04-21上課內容練習","tags":"Misc"}]};